-- Supports:
-- Title empty by default
-- Left icon / Close icon
-- Themes: Dark, Red, Aqua, Light
-- Discord banner + link
-- Tabs, Sections, Buttons, Toggles, Sliders, Dropdowns, Notify
-- Icon support via ImageId or icon map (Lucide names -> ImageId)

